<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="suitable-adj">suitable <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'suːtəbl, 'sjuːtəbl/    美 /'suːtəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>适合的；适宜的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t have anything <strong>suitable to</strong> wear for the party.
我没有适合在晚会上穿的衣服。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This programme is not <strong>suitable for</strong> children.
这个节目儿童不宜。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not all men <strong>are suitable for</strong> that kind of work. 
不是所有的人都适合从事那类工作。</p></div></div>